<li><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.snopes.com/language/apocryph/pluckyew.asp">"Pluck Yew"</a>. <i><a href="../Snopes.com" title="Snopes.com">Snopes.com</a></i>. July 9, 2007<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.snopes.com/language/apocryph/pluckyew.asp">http://www.snopes.com/language/apocryph/pluckyew.asp</a></span>.</span></li>
</ul>
